72
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:59,220
[SPEAKER_03] To je, pazi, podzemlje, ne može mirovati na to.

73
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:04,700
[SPEAKER_03] I to su, mislim, uvijek s post festom to bude ono, mizerni trzaj,

74
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:07,440
