871
00:52:56,079 --> 00:52:59,139
[SPEAKER_03] ali evo tu su sad umjetnici koji nešto progovaraju,

872
00:52:59,139 --> 00:53:03,219
[SPEAKER_03] jer, da, da, da, da, da, da, ne, ne još, ne još,

873
00:53:03,219 --> 00:53:05,559
[SPEAKER_03] Bog sam zna kako će se stvari rešavati,

874
00:53:05,559 --> 00:53:07,599
[SPEAKER_03] te rane kad budu za rasle jednog dana,

875
00:53:07,599 --> 00:53:10,380
[SPEAKER_03] i kada se dogode te katarse koje su potrebne,

876
00:53:10,380 --> 00:53:13,420
[SPEAKER_03] na koncu molimo i za te stvari,

877
00:53:13,420 --> 00:53:17,280
[SPEAKER_03] pogledat će, pogledat će vrativni predstav,

878
00:53:17,280 --> 00:53:19,940
[SPEAKER_03] i ako kažem, bilo je, bilo je, već i ja znam,

879
00:53:20,039 --> 00:53:22,400
[SPEAKER_03] osobno iz svog nekog kruga poznanstava,

880
00:53:22,400 --> 00:53:24,280
[SPEAKER_03] i nekih novih koje sam baš upoznal,

881
00:53:24,280 --> 00:53:26,320
[SPEAKER_03] poslije predstava baš Srba,

882
00:53:26,320 --> 00:53:28,559
[SPEAKER_03] koji su pogledali već predstavo i ovamo,

883
00:53:28,559 --> 00:53:30,300
[SPEAKER_03] i koji su tako oduševljeni bili,

884
00:53:30,300 --> 00:53:32,960
[SPEAKER_03] koji su tako oduševljeni bili,

885
00:53:32,960 --> 00:53:34,940
[SPEAKER_03] koji su baš, evo, baš,

886
00:53:34,940 --> 00:53:37,820
[SPEAKER_03] je jedan od njih rekao da je predstava baš melem,

887
00:53:37,820 --> 00:53:41,599
[SPEAKER_03] melem ne samo za nas kao za žrtvu,

888
00:53:41,599 --> 00:53:43,199
[SPEAKER_03] kaže, ne samo za vas kao za žrtvu,

889
00:53:43,199 --> 00:53:44,760
[SPEAKER_03] nego, evo, i za mene,

890
00:53:44,760 --> 00:53:48,079
[SPEAKER_03] koji sam pripadnik naroda koji je počinio ta zlodjela,

891
00:53:49,139 --> 00:53:52,480
[SPEAKER_03] jer meni jako znači da se naslonim tu na te vrane,

892
00:53:52,480 --> 00:53:55,760
[SPEAKER_03] da ispravno vrednujem tu prošlost.

893
00:53:55,760 --> 00:53:57,519
[SPEAKER_03] I evo, mislim da je tu taj ključ,

894
00:53:57,519 --> 00:53:59,239
[SPEAKER_03] zato kažem da je umjetnost jako važna,

895
00:53:59,239 --> 00:54:02,579
[SPEAKER_03] i zato je jako važno da se ti talenti njeguju od samog starta,

896
00:54:02,579 --> 00:54:05,980
[SPEAKER_03] da te nove pridružene snage mogu raditi na toj Boži odnjivi,

897
00:54:05,980 --> 00:54:07,780
[SPEAKER_03] kako mi katolici to volimo reći.

898
00:54:08,500 --> 00:54:11,039
[SPEAKER_03] A koliko je predstava utjecala na tebe samog?

899
00:54:11,039 --> 00:54:15,960
[SPEAKER_03] Pa, predstava je utjecala u toliko što mi je otvorila nekako pogled novina,

900
00:54:15,960 --> 00:54:20,739
[SPEAKER_03] umjetnost, tu sam zapravo se poprilično istesa kao glumac,

901
00:54:21,340 --> 00:54:25,519
[SPEAKER_03] jer to je najzahtjevnija kazališna forma,

902
00:54:25,519 --> 00:54:26,840
[SPEAKER_03] si sam na sceni,

903
00:54:26,840 --> 00:54:30,199
[SPEAKER_03] sat i dvadeset i na tiku pomoću,

904
00:54:30,199 --> 00:54:32,739
[SPEAKER_03] i sve ideš dijelom iz sebe,

905
00:54:32,739 --> 00:54:34,619
[SPEAKER_03] dijelom iz tih očiju koje te gledaju.

906
00:54:34,619 --> 00:54:36,199
[SPEAKER_03] I otvorilo mi je nekako,

907
00:54:36,199 --> 00:54:39,199
[SPEAKER_03] drilajući tu moju sposobnost,

908
00:54:39,199 --> 00:54:41,400
[SPEAKER_03] te moje scenske snalažljivosti,

909
00:54:41,400 --> 00:54:44,760
[SPEAKER_03] da zapravo shvatim koliko moj život,

910
00:54:44,760 --> 00:54:47,300
[SPEAKER_03] kovo Marko, što sam ti rekao za tom stano,

911
00:54:47,300 --> 00:54:48,860
[SPEAKER_03] kako mu je vidjelo da mu je križ,

912
00:54:48,860 --> 00:54:51,679
[SPEAKER_03] unio emociju koji prije nije imao glas,

913
00:54:51,679 --> 00:54:54,579
[SPEAKER_03] tako je jednostavno neke priče iz Vukovara,

914
00:54:54,579 --> 00:54:56,880
[SPEAKER_03] kako sam ja životno sazrijevao

915
00:54:56,880 --> 00:55:01,019
[SPEAKER_03] i kako sam dolazio neke druge životne postaje

916
00:55:01,019 --> 00:55:02,599
[SPEAKER_03] koje su me odonijeli djecu tu,

917
00:55:02,599 --> 00:55:03,679
[SPEAKER_03] evo sad troje djece,

918
00:55:04,440 --> 00:55:05,059
[SPEAKER_03] ja vidim,

919
00:55:05,059 --> 00:55:07,659
[SPEAKER_03] ta djeca su mi pomogla,

920
00:55:07,659 --> 00:55:08,679
[SPEAKER_03] čak su u jednoj priči,

921
00:55:08,679 --> 00:55:10,519
[SPEAKER_03] to jednoj interpretaciji,

922
00:55:10,519 --> 00:55:12,360
[SPEAKER_03] odnosno toj scenskoj tidi,

923
00:55:12,360 --> 00:55:15,039
[SPEAKER_03] čak pričan jedan događaj s svoje kuće

924
00:55:15,039 --> 00:55:17,039
[SPEAKER_03] sa Stipom i Marijom Faustinom.

925
00:55:17,039 --> 00:55:20,159
[SPEAKER_03] I to bude jedan moment stand-up

926
00:55:20,159 --> 00:55:21,119
[SPEAKER_03] usred predstave,

927
00:55:21,119 --> 00:55:24,539
[SPEAKER_03] ali se naslanja na sinnišinu priču o igri.

928
00:55:24,539 --> 00:55:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači predstava imala neki promjene?

929
00:55:27,340 --> 00:55:28,599
[SPEAKER_03] Ona ima, da, da,

930
00:55:28,599 --> 00:55:30,300
[SPEAKER_03] ona imala nekoliko tih svojih promjene,

931
00:55:30,300 --> 00:55:31,519
[SPEAKER_03] rednostavno kako živim,

932
00:55:31,519 --> 00:55:32,820
[SPEAKER_03] kako sazrijevam,

933
00:55:34,260 --> 00:55:38,820
[SPEAKER_03] ako tu dobivam neku tu nove životne dimenzije,

934
00:55:38,820 --> 00:55:41,320
[SPEAKER_03] normalno da osjećaš potrebu kao umjetnik,

935
00:55:41,320 --> 00:55:46,320
[SPEAKER_03] to injektirat nekako u taj tekst,

936
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:47,820
[SPEAKER_03] da on bude puno krvanje,

937
00:55:47,820 --> 00:55:48,719
[SPEAKER_03] da bude životan.

938
00:55:49,159 --> 00:55:51,780
[SPEAKER_03] a životan je samo ako te se tiče do kraja, razumiješ?

939
00:55:52,380 --> 00:55:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] tvoja druga monodrama,

940
00:55:53,699 --> 00:55:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam tamo,

941
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] po motivima tunike,

942
00:55:57,000 --> 00:55:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] Lloyd C. Douglas.

943
00:55:58,239 --> 00:56:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tri puta gledao toju prestao i...

944
00:56:03,059 --> 00:56:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] i odlučio se da ćeš uskočiti,

945
00:56:05,300 --> 00:56:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto mene kaja ne bude mogla...

946
00:56:06,900 --> 00:56:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] bit ćemo još malo da...

947
00:56:09,079 --> 00:56:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Skoro znam sa tekst, pa onda imao ga i bar sam...

948
00:56:11,579 --> 00:56:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, to sam htio reći,

949
00:56:14,000 --> 00:56:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] nijedna izvedba nije ista i svaki put se zakačiš za nešto drugo,

950
00:56:19,460 --> 00:56:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] neki drugi trenutak te zapani i ostavi u razmišljanju.

951
00:56:25,739 --> 00:56:28,739
[SPEAKER_03] Pa zato što, eto, to je to pitanje životnosti.

952
00:56:28,739 --> 00:56:33,619
[SPEAKER_03] I ti u životnosti nemaš, uvijek, znaš,

953
00:56:33,619 --> 00:56:35,460
[SPEAKER_03] Biblija je knjiga života.

954
00:56:35,460 --> 00:56:42,039
[SPEAKER_03] Biblija je knjiga života i ti u knjizi života uvijek možeš na istoj priči

955
00:56:42,039 --> 00:56:46,679
[SPEAKER_03] svaki put drugačije nešto viditi, drugačiju poruku isrpiti.

956
00:56:46,679 --> 00:56:48,780
[SPEAKER_03] I zato je knjiga života životnost.

957
00:56:48,780 --> 00:56:53,280
[SPEAKER_03] I kad tu životnost uneseš u neke druge djelatne sfere,

958
00:56:53,280 --> 00:56:54,840
[SPEAKER_03] pa evo, recimo, sama predstava,

959
00:56:55,300 --> 00:56:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] ona je naslonjena na priču, na otajstu velikog petka

960
00:56:58,000 --> 00:57:03,739
[SPEAKER_03] i ta jedan mučni put kroz te postaje,

961
00:57:03,739 --> 00:57:10,760
[SPEAKER_03] od Alito Stratosa do Kalvarije, do Golgote i tog križa,

962
00:57:10,760 --> 00:57:14,780
[SPEAKER_03] ti zapravo imaš priču naših života,

963
00:57:14,780 --> 00:57:19,300
[SPEAKER_03] gdje se čovjek neprestano pita, jesam li ja bio tamo?

964
00:57:19,300 --> 00:57:22,300
[SPEAKER_03] Znači kako se razvija ta čovjekova svijest

965
00:57:22,300 --> 00:57:26,460
[SPEAKER_03] o spasenju, o otkupljenju, o triumfu Uskrsa,

966
00:57:26,460 --> 00:57:29,239
[SPEAKER_03] koji je neminovan bez smrti?

967
00:57:29,239 --> 00:57:33,500
[SPEAKER_03] Kako je bilo zgodno da možeš prihskočiti taj petak nekako,

968
00:57:33,500 --> 00:57:38,780
[SPEAKER_03] pa da sa tih, iz te Galileje, nekako iz tih divnih putova,

969
00:57:38,780 --> 00:57:42,920
[SPEAKER_03] činjanja čudesa, ozdravljanja, zacjeljivanja, uha, dizanja,

970
00:57:43,059 --> 00:57:47,039
[SPEAKER_03] kromih i vraćanja vida slijepima, da je moguće o tu samo skočiti

971
00:57:47,039 --> 00:57:52,639
[SPEAKER_03] ispred tog razvaljenog kamena i vidjet triumf Uskrsloga u nebu.

972
00:57:52,639 --> 00:57:58,280
[SPEAKER_03] E, ali da bi došao do tu, treba neminovno proći kroz taj križni put

973
00:57:58,280 --> 00:58:01,480
[SPEAKER_03] i zapravo je tu ono gdje smo mi pozvali.

974
00:58:01,539 --> 00:58:04,219
[SPEAKER_03] Zato nije ta predstava, ona nije ugodna za gledat.

975
00:58:04,219 --> 00:58:07,760
[SPEAKER_03] Kad ti sjedneš, tebe neće čekat ugoda do kraja.

976
00:58:07,760 --> 00:58:13,579
[SPEAKER_03] Zato tu, ja sam zaista doživio jedno pešest puta

977
00:58:13,579 --> 00:58:16,860
[SPEAKER_03] da su se ljudi digli, da su otišli, i to ne pred kraj.

978
00:58:16,860 --> 00:58:20,039
[SPEAKER_03] Pa da možeš pomisli, znaš, bilo je ovaj...

979
00:58:20,039 --> 00:58:21,420
[SPEAKER_03] Žurlojim se negdje moralo se...

980
00:58:21,420 --> 00:58:23,400
[SPEAKER_03] Znaš, žurloj se ili kao daš, dosadno mi je.

981
00:58:23,400 --> 00:58:27,440
[SPEAKER_03] Nego negdje, prije sredine, cijelo vrijeme,

982
00:58:27,440 --> 00:58:29,659
[SPEAKER_03] i pogotovo taj djelj koji je vrlo dinamičan,

983
00:58:29,980 --> 00:58:32,199
[SPEAKER_03] gdje on opisuje, zapravo Marcel Galli,

984
00:58:32,199 --> 00:58:34,440
[SPEAKER_03] ili lik tog rimskog centurina,

985
00:58:34,440 --> 00:58:37,780
[SPEAKER_03] opisuje doslovno sistem, princip mučenja.

986
00:58:37,780 --> 00:58:41,880
[SPEAKER_03] Kako je to išlo, i te i te ta lokva krvi

987
00:58:41,880 --> 00:58:44,639
[SPEAKER_03] u toj malom matriumu, zakažnjavanju i to.

988
00:58:44,639 --> 00:58:46,119
[SPEAKER_03] I ljudima je to neugodno.

989
00:58:46,119 --> 00:58:49,980
[SPEAKER_03] Slušaj, ne želim biti dio toga, idem čak...

990
00:58:49,980 --> 00:58:51,860
[SPEAKER_03] Znaš, i to je nezgodno, neugodno.

991
00:58:51,860 --> 00:58:53,559
[SPEAKER_03] I da je moguće priskočiti, znaš,

992
00:58:53,559 --> 00:58:55,039
[SPEAKER_03] i sad vidite ovoga, znaš, tako kažem,

993
00:58:55,039 --> 00:58:56,780
[SPEAKER_03] pasija je jedan od najručnijih filmova.

994
00:58:58,420 --> 00:59:00,599
[SPEAKER_03] Ali isto od mnog i preljep.

995
00:59:00,599 --> 00:59:03,780
[SPEAKER_03] Jer istinit, znaš, jer ti vidiš

996
00:59:03,780 --> 00:59:07,139
[SPEAKER_03] u onome susretu njega i majke,

997
00:59:07,139 --> 00:59:08,119
[SPEAKER_03] to je najtužnija,

998
00:59:08,119 --> 00:59:10,059
[SPEAKER_03] meni najemotivnija cena,

999
00:59:10,059 --> 00:59:11,599
[SPEAKER_03] sednu umjetnost ikada,

1000
00:59:11,599 --> 00:59:12,940
[SPEAKER_03] od kada je izmišljena kamera.

1001
00:59:12,940 --> 00:59:16,940
[SPEAKER_03] I ti vidiš da je taj cijeli krišni put

1002
00:59:16,940 --> 00:59:19,760
[SPEAKER_03] stavljen u tu rečenicu,

1003
00:59:19,760 --> 00:59:21,139
[SPEAKER_03] majku, vidi, činim sve novo.

1004
00:59:21,139 --> 00:59:23,800
[SPEAKER_03] E to novo, taj triumf jednog dana,

1005
00:59:23,800 --> 00:59:24,760
[SPEAKER_03] to ne možeš ga,

1006
00:59:24,760 --> 00:59:27,300
[SPEAKER_03] ne možeš ga dosjeći bez činjenja.

1007
00:59:27,300 --> 00:59:29,940
[SPEAKER_03] Vidi, majku, činim, sad činim sve novo.

1008
00:59:29,940 --> 00:59:31,360
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, moraš proći

1009
00:59:31,360 --> 00:59:33,360
[SPEAKER_03] taj križni put, da, da bi moglo

1010
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:34,940
[SPEAKER_03] doći do, do, do, do, do,

1011
00:59:34,940 --> 00:59:36,519
[SPEAKER_03] do pobjede.

1012
00:59:36,519 --> 00:59:38,599
[SPEAKER_03] I zato je ovo ta monodrama,

1013
00:59:38,599 --> 00:59:40,539
[SPEAKER_03] koja je nastala u tom,

1014
00:59:40,539 --> 00:59:42,679
[SPEAKER_03] najsušnijem razdoblju moga nekakog života,

1015
00:59:42,679 --> 00:59:46,360
[SPEAKER_03] i u tom jednom molitvojnom siromaštu.

1016
00:59:46,360 --> 00:59:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kako je ukće nastala?

1017
00:59:47,519 --> 00:59:50,940
[SPEAKER_03] Pa evo, ja sam to u više navrata

1018
00:59:50,940 --> 00:59:53,599
[SPEAKER_03] baš bio priča, ovoga,

1019
00:59:53,599 --> 00:59:57,099
[SPEAKER_03] to je bilo, korizma je bila,

1020
00:59:57,099 --> 00:59:58,460
[SPEAKER_03] ja sam prolazio jednu, jednu,

1021
00:59:58,460 --> 00:59:59,860
[SPEAKER_03] jednu dosta težak period,

1022
00:59:59,860 --> 01:00:01,039
[SPEAKER_03] nisan igrao kazalištu.

1023
01:00:01,039 --> 01:00:03,840
[SPEAKER_03] Tada je bilo skoro dvije godine,

1024
01:00:03,840 --> 01:00:05,219
[SPEAKER_03] iz nekog razloga,

1025
01:00:05,219 --> 01:00:06,199
[SPEAKER_03] evo, mene nema više,

1026
01:00:06,199 --> 01:00:06,820
[SPEAKER_03] i to je to.

1027
01:00:06,820 --> 01:00:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] Oka plaća, sjeda, mene nema.

1028
01:00:09,000 --> 01:00:10,739
[SPEAKER_03] I to boli u frustraciju.

1029
01:00:10,739 --> 01:00:11,500
[SPEAKER_03] Sam pali to.

1030
01:00:11,900 --> 01:00:12,380
[SPEAKER_03] E, molim.

1031
01:00:12,380 --> 01:00:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] Šta pali i tome.

1032
01:00:13,579 --> 01:00:14,639
[SPEAKER_03] E, to su rekli.

1033
01:00:14,639 --> 01:00:17,199
[SPEAKER_03] To je taj, danesni mentalitet.

1034
01:00:17,199 --> 01:00:18,800
[SPEAKER_03] Socialistički san čovječe,

1035
01:00:18,800 --> 01:00:19,920
[SPEAKER_03] ovo je svi da plaća,

1036
01:00:19,920 --> 01:00:21,219
[SPEAKER_03] ti ne mrdaš prstake,

1037
01:00:21,219 --> 01:00:21,920
[SPEAKER_03] kućaš bolje,

1038
01:00:21,920 --> 01:00:23,139
[SPEAKER_03] što se budalo javljaš,

1039
01:00:23,139 --> 01:00:23,659
[SPEAKER_03] nije, to treba,

1040
01:00:23,659 --> 01:00:25,559
[SPEAKER_03] stano si na zadovoljan života,

1041
01:00:25,559 --> 01:00:25,940
[SPEAKER_03] znaš.

1042
01:00:25,940 --> 01:00:27,300
[SPEAKER_03] Ja, to je poslje,

1043
01:00:27,300 --> 01:00:28,300
[SPEAKER_03] Bog u mom životu,

1044
01:00:28,300 --> 01:00:29,659
[SPEAKER_03] u taboru izlječio,

1045
01:00:29,659 --> 01:00:31,199
[SPEAKER_03] gospodin da jednostavno

1046
01:00:31,199 --> 01:00:32,980
[SPEAKER_03] sve te moje frustracije je zalječio,

1047
01:00:32,980 --> 01:00:35,480
[SPEAKER_03] da mi ja više ne ovisim nikad o tome.

1048
01:00:35,480 --> 01:00:38,239
[SPEAKER_03] O tome, o ulogama,

1049
01:00:38,239 --> 01:00:39,019
[SPEAKER_03] i nikad neću,

1050
01:00:41,900 --> 01:00:42,699
[SPEAKER_03] nikad,

1051
01:00:42,699 --> 01:00:44,480
[SPEAKER_03] a uvijek ću puštano izdušavati svoj posao,

1052
01:00:44,480 --> 01:00:44,900
[SPEAKER_03] uvijek.

1053
01:00:44,900 --> 01:00:46,679
[SPEAKER_03] I ovoga,

1054
01:00:46,679 --> 01:00:49,519
[SPEAKER_03] i ja nekako frustriranaš,

1055
01:00:49,519 --> 01:00:50,059
[SPEAKER_03] ne igram,

1056
01:00:50,059 --> 01:00:51,300
[SPEAKER_03] jedna uloga me maši,

1057
01:00:51,300 --> 01:00:52,199
[SPEAKER_03] druga me maši,

1058
01:00:52,199 --> 01:00:52,860
[SPEAKER_03] neke dvije žene,

1059
01:00:52,860 --> 01:00:53,739
[SPEAKER_03] tamo sam malo smirio,

1060
01:00:53,739 --> 01:00:54,320
[SPEAKER_03] bio dva dana,

1061
01:00:54,320 --> 01:00:56,219
[SPEAKER_03] neke dvije žene me srela u gradu,

1062
01:00:56,219 --> 01:00:57,079
[SPEAKER_03] a prostite,

1063
01:00:57,079 --> 01:00:58,579
[SPEAKER_03] vi više ne radite tu,

1064
01:00:58,579 --> 01:00:59,139
[SPEAKER_03] jel' tako?

1065
01:00:59,139 --> 01:01:00,280
[SPEAKER_03] Ja, ono,

1066
01:01:00,280 --> 01:01:02,019
[SPEAKER_03] no,

1067
01:01:02,019 --> 01:01:02,900
[SPEAKER_03] di me nađe,

1068
01:01:02,900 --> 01:01:04,719
[SPEAKER_03] bako.

1069
01:01:05,639 --> 01:01:05,860
[SPEAKER_03] ja gledam,

1070
01:01:05,860 --> 01:01:06,980
[SPEAKER_03] to je sad tako ja govorim,

1071
01:01:06,980 --> 01:01:07,760
[SPEAKER_03] to ide onako,

1072
01:01:07,760 --> 01:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] ciklički ja govorim,

1073
01:01:09,000 --> 01:01:10,079
[SPEAKER_03] u doći opet prilike,

1074
01:01:10,079 --> 01:01:10,880
[SPEAKER_03] moramo se malo,

1075
01:01:10,880 --> 01:01:12,159
[SPEAKER_03] ono će se rastrestan sam,

1076
01:01:12,159 --> 01:01:13,320
[SPEAKER_03] bit će dobro sve to.

1077
01:01:13,320 --> 01:01:15,360
[SPEAKER_03] Uteka ja,

1078
01:01:15,360 --> 01:01:16,280
[SPEAKER_03] i uglavnom,

1079
01:01:16,280 --> 01:01:17,800
[SPEAKER_03] jako frustriran,

1080
01:01:17,800 --> 01:01:19,519
[SPEAKER_03] ne molim,

1081
01:01:19,519 --> 01:01:20,440
[SPEAKER_03] moja Katarina,

1082
01:01:20,440 --> 01:01:20,920
[SPEAKER_03] ajme,

1083
01:01:20,920 --> 01:01:21,480
[SPEAKER_03] korizma,

1084
