[SPEAKER_03] je milosno vrijeme,

1087
01:01:24,320 --> 01:01:25,699
[SPEAKER_03] to je milosno,

1088
01:01:25,699 --> 01:01:26,079
[SPEAKER_03] i sad,

1089
