[SPEAKER_03] nisu oni meniti,

1113
01:01:48,539 --> 01:01:49,239
[SPEAKER_03] ja sve to znam,

1114
01:01:49,239 --> 01:01:50,699
[SPEAKER_03] ali zašto je korizma milosno vrijeme,

1115
01:01:50,699 --> 01:01:51,639
[SPEAKER_03] zašto nije milosno vrijeme,

1116
01:01:51,639 --> 01:01:53,059
[SPEAKER_03] od 9. do 10. mjeseca,

1117
01:01:53,059 --> 01:01:54,920
[SPEAKER_03] i onda se dogodi,

1118
01:01:54,920 --> 01:01:55,599
[SPEAKER_03] ja sam odlučio,

1119
01:01:55,599 --> 01:01:56,519
[SPEAKER_03] na početku korizme,

1120
01:01:56,519 --> 01:01:58,800
[SPEAKER_03] da ću pročitat Tuniku Daglasovu,

1121
01:01:58,800 --> 01:01:59,940
[SPEAKER_03] do Uskrsa,

1122
01:01:59,940 --> 01:02:02,019
[SPEAKER_03] kao neki zadatak,

1123
01:02:02,019 --> 01:02:03,659
[SPEAKER_03] sebi koji sam dao,

1124
01:02:03,659 --> 01:02:05,420
[SPEAKER_03] i onda odem,

1125
