1132
01:02:19,739 --> 01:02:21,800
[SPEAKER_03] i zamišljam,

1133
01:02:21,800 --> 01:02:23,219
[SPEAKER_03] kao bi Katarina izgledali,

1134
01:02:23,579 --> 01:02:25,360
[SPEAKER_03] da smo sad na mjesto tih roditelja,

1135
01:02:25,360 --> 01:02:26,420
[SPEAKER_03] i sad,

1136
01:02:26,420 --> 01:02:26,739
[SPEAKER_03] naš,

1137
01:02:26,739 --> 01:02:27,579
[SPEAKER_03] ja kad sam to sve dočio,

1138
01:02:27,579 --> 01:02:28,139
[SPEAKER_03] okolo pitali mi,

1139
01:02:28,139 --> 01:02:28,980
[SPEAKER_03] da sam ti normalan,

1140
01:02:28,980 --> 01:02:29,159
[SPEAKER_03] zašto,

1141
01:02:29,159 --> 01:02:29,840
[SPEAKER_03] ja ko ne znam,

1142
