[SPEAKER_03] prije sad navijao da te misle dođu,

1143
01:02:32,139 --> 01:02:33,320
[SPEAKER_03] samo su dolazile,

1144
01:02:33,320 --> 01:02:34,460
[SPEAKER_03] ti ljudi,

1145
01:02:34,460 --> 01:02:35,260
[SPEAKER_03] je tajsto smrti,

1146
01:02:35,260 --> 01:02:36,840
[SPEAKER_03] mi ne moramo se susretat s tim,

1147
01:02:36,840 --> 01:02:38,679
[SPEAKER_03] pozicionirati sebe,

1148
01:02:38,679 --> 01:02:39,000
[SPEAKER_03] naš,

1149
01:02:39,000 --> 01:02:40,820
[SPEAKER_03] to je neki sadomazohizam,

1150
01:02:40,820 --> 01:02:41,099
[SPEAKER_03] ono,

1151
01:02:41,099 --> 01:02:41,579
[SPEAKER_03] ko da kaže,

1152
01:02:41,579 --> 01:02:42,940
[SPEAKER_03] ja se osjećaš bol tu,

1153
01:02:42,940 --> 01:02:44,079
[SPEAKER_03] ali hoćeš proći,

1154
01:02:44,079 --> 01:02:44,519
[SPEAKER_03] kroz tu vidjeti,

1155
01:02:44,519 --> 01:02:45,519
[SPEAKER_03] zamisliti sve do kraja,

1156
01:02:45,519 --> 01:02:47,760
[SPEAKER_03] i ova,

1157
01:02:47,760 --> 01:02:48,360
[SPEAKER_03] i ja

1158
01:02:48,360 --> 01:02:51,019
[SPEAKER_03] se vratim sa tog sprovoda,

1159
01:02:51,019 --> 01:02:51,920
[SPEAKER_03] uzmem tu knjigu,

1160
01:02:51,920 --> 01:02:54,039
[SPEAKER_03] i krenem i čitam dalje,

1161
01:02:54,039 --> 01:02:55,360
[SPEAKER_03] tamo sam došao njeg do pola,

1162
01:02:55,360 --> 01:02:57,500
[SPEAKER_03] čujemo ga,

1163
01:02:57,500 --> 01:02:58,219
[SPEAKER_03] u sebi glas,

1164
