[SPEAKER_03] idi i napravi,

1165
01:02:59,039 --> 01:03:01,719
[SPEAKER_03] što ja dam koga da napravim,

1166
01:03:01,719 --> 01:03:02,139
[SPEAKER_03] dano što,

1167
01:03:02,139 --> 01:03:02,579
[SPEAKER_03] što,

1168
