1173
01:03:10,900 --> 01:03:13,440
[SPEAKER_03] gdje se nateo napraviti monodramu o punciju Pilatu,

1174
01:03:13,440 --> 01:03:16,719
[SPEAKER_03] kao od noć prije donošenja odluke,

1175
01:03:16,719 --> 01:03:18,559
[SPEAKER_03] što je on prolazio sa svom ženom,

1176
01:03:18,559 --> 01:03:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] znaš,

1177
01:03:19,000 --> 01:03:19,360
[SPEAKER_03] ovo,

1178
01:03:19,360 --> 01:03:22,619
[SPEAKER_03] koja je imala simpatiju prema Isusu,

1179
01:03:22,619 --> 01:03:24,480
