1185
01:03:33,019 --> 01:03:34,440
[SPEAKER_03] zapravo ta monodramada,

1186
01:03:34,440 --> 01:03:35,619
[SPEAKER_03] to ne treba biti,

1187
01:03:35,619 --> 01:03:37,380
[SPEAKER_03] to nije politička takva priča,

1188
01:03:37,380 --> 01:03:38,199
[SPEAKER_03] dakle, znači,

1189
01:03:38,199 --> 01:03:40,539
[SPEAKER_03] ime biti protka na političkom nekom konotaciju,

1190
01:03:40,539 --> 01:03:41,400
[SPEAKER_03] na nekim sferama,

1191
01:03:41,400 --> 01:03:42,920
[SPEAKER_03] ali ne priča o Pilatu,

1192
01:03:42,920 --> 01:03:44,260
[SPEAKER_03] jer Pilat je institucija,

1193
01:03:44,260 --> 01:03:44,760
[SPEAKER_03] on je,

1194
01:03:44,760 --> 01:03:45,320
[SPEAKER_03] on je,

1195
01:03:45,320 --> 01:03:46,320
[SPEAKER_03] on je,

1196
01:03:46,320 --> 01:03:47,659
[SPEAKER_03] on je nedohvatljiv,

1197
01:03:47,659 --> 01:03:48,840
[SPEAKER_03] jer je to visoka politika,

1198
01:03:48,840 --> 01:03:50,800
[SPEAKER_03] to mora biti prljavština ulice,

1199
01:03:50,800 --> 01:03:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] vojnik koji vodi razbojnički garnizon,

1200
01:03:54,000 --> 01:03:55,619
[SPEAKER_03] doslovno neuredne pijance,

1201
01:03:55,619 --> 01:03:56,800
[SPEAKER_03] koje treba dovesti u red,

1202
01:03:56,800 --> 01:03:58,860
